title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland Auditorium Arena on 1979-12-31
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw-> Franklin's Tower, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, Tennessee Jed, Looks Like Rain-> Alabama Getaway-> Promised Land

Set 2

Sugar Magnolia-> China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Samson & Delilah, Ship of Fools, Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Deal

Set 3

Althea-> Minglewood Blues, Uncle John's Band-> Drums-> Not Fade Away*-> Stella Blue*-> Sunshine Daydream*, E: Good Lovin'

*W John Cippolina Other artist(s): Richard Olson, Flying Karamozov Brothers

reviews.review_text: Nice long show, quality suffers This would've been the show to go to!  Now all I can hope for is for Dark Star Orchestra to re-create this one sometime when I'm there.  The sound quality with all the patches kinda suffers.
